{"tid":2319604,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴疑似抽水：曼聯是歐霸大熱","createTime":"2020-12-10T08:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T01:00:02.000Z","uid":19552,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4ed02f67be732161fdc076d71be1fc9645118370","tid":2319604,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T08:14:47.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】曼聯剛於歐聯出局，轉戰歐霸盃，前領隊摩連奴立即指他們是奪標大熱，有挖苦之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n摩連奴（Jose Mourinho）帶領的熱刺早已在歐霸盃出線32強，之後有機會遇上前東家曼聯，他說：「那些從歐聯被淘汰的都是強隊，通常不屬於歐霸盃的水准。」 「曼聯是頂級球隊之一，身處的小組很難踢，對任何一隊都不容易。」摩佬在2017年曾經帶領紅魔贏得歐霸盃冠軍。 熱刺今季的表現遠勝曼聯，於英超高踞榜首，摩連奴盛讚一對前鋒：「我在每家球會都有出色的前鋒，有些是純粹的射手，另一些則做得更多。哈利簡尼、孫興敏很特別，永遠以團隊為先。」 熱刺周四在最後一輪分組賽將於主場迎戰安特衛普，摩佬證實右閘奧希爾、中場靴爾保避戰，至於翼鋒林美拉在1月才能夠復出。"},{"pid":"a6b40e5c65d6f51603a9e7398c4ec1b8a05bd53a","tid":2319604,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":33,"score":-33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"大方啲啦幾廿歲人"},{"pid":"10f9b199196ce793b2d2fc122287d455b003b8e7","tid":2319604,"uid":191811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2ec1be8a06538a10a7b938be139562edddd227","tid":2319604,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T10:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac7a10c55a7cac7d9e6de81f3b0a41bf3f9182b","tid":2319604,"uid":173952,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T10:14:12.000Z","msg":"讚對手奪標大熱,又屈人抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAC米蘭貴為意甲榜首,唔提佢咪仲串"},{"pid":"06798ad21bfa55ad5ba72d3b81eeacaa9de63782","tid":2319604,"uid":238369,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T10:15:27.000Z","msg":"讚你又話串，49000真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"